title: How to Manifest The Life You Want
itunes:title: How to Manifest The Life You Want
description:
My mom has always joked with me that I get everything I want. I feel it's because the opposite of what I want doesn't exist in my reality. In this episode, I am going to teach you about that mindset and how it will help you manifest what you want in your life.
